snippet.title: Best VGM 748 - Tekken 6 - Yodeling in Meadow Hill (Hidden Retreat)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS3 / Xbox 360 / Arcade / PSP
Tekken 6 (2009)
Yodeling in Meadow Hill (Hidden Retreat)
Keiichi Okabe
